Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(1182.4,608.2)}Potret Diri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selamat bersenang-senang...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selamat bersenang-senang...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mari bersenang-senanglah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ujian tahap pertama untuk jurusan\N {\i1}lukis cat minyak{\i0} Universitas Seni Tokyo, dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Boleh dimulai.
